                  Warning Notice


Since you are even contemplating using this program, certain 
things about you and your operation are assumed at this point:

You are intimately familiar with the liability you are taking 
on your own accord.  Industrial machinery and other equipment 
that can be controlled by PLCs and other such industrial machinery
can be extremely dangerous.  It is not uncommon for this machinery 
to be capable of severely injuring or KILLING people.  

THIS PROGRAM IS CAPABLE OF MODIFYING THE INTERNAL CONTENTS OF THE 
DATA TABLE OF A PLC.  THAT CAN CAUSE YOUR MACHINERY TO ACTIVATE OR 
OTHERWISE OPERATE IN AN UNPREDICTABLE AND/OR DANGEROUS MANNER.  
IT IS ENTIRELY YOUR RESPONSIBILITY TO BE CERTAIN THAT THIS PROGRAM 
DOES NOT CAUSE YOUR MACHINERY TO OPERATE IN AN UNSAFE MANNER. 

